text.headline: Launch Day
text.text: I am a one-man team and still a student. I am still trying to figure out how this app will fit in the world, but I am looking forward to the journey.

text.headline: Select & Analyze Release Day
text.text: On this significant day, we are thrilled to unveil a groundbreaking feature known as 'Select & Analyze.' With this remarkable addition, users gain the power to navigate an extensive player database, enabling them to effortlessly explore and delve into comprehensive statistics spanning the entire season.
